N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 451.127 - Fund group

State Regulations
A group of funds of similar character which are brought
together for administrative and reporting purposes. Examples: current funds; loan funds; endowment funds; plant funds; agency funds. Notes
